<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-165-008 </DOCNO><DOCID>10 727 683</DOCID><JOURNAL>Lotus  May 1991 v7 n5 p85(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Lotus Publishing Corp. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>The Judd Test: measuring 1-2-3 proficiency. (Mentrix's The JuddTest for Lotus 1-2-3.) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Ray, Garry.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Mentrix Corp. (Product introduction).andO;Product:   The Judd Test for Lotus 1-2-3 (Add-in/on software) (Productintroduction).andO;Topic:     Add-In/On SoftwareTestingPerformance MeasurementJob PerformanceProduct Introduction.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>&quot;Know how to use 1-2-3'.?&quot; &quot;Yup-just like the back of my hand.&quot;andM;That conversation is repeated thousands of times each day in businessesacross the land.andP;  Yet both parties may be disappointed when they realize thatknowing 1-2-3&quot; implies an enormous range of skill levels, from tyro to expertmacro writer.andM;The Judd Test for Lotus 1-2-3 is an evaluation package that makes it easy toset things straight.andP;  By testing users for a broad range of 1-2-3 skillsthrough standardized spreadsheet tasks, the package can tell you how anyemployee--current or prospective-really rates in 1-2-3 knowledge.andM;The program looks at about 20 types of 1-2-3 skills, including copying,moving, and erasing cell ranges.andP;  Other tests focus on spreadsheet links, thehelp system, printing, and graphics facilities.andP;  More advanced users can bechallenged on their understanding of macros, @functions, formulas, anddatabase commands.andM;Each test is presented in an identical manner.andP;  After the test isautomatically set up within the spreadsheet, a small instruction windowappears on the screen, telling you what task to complete.andP;  You signalcompletion by typing an exclamation point.andM;The package tries to measure the efficiency of a 1-2-3 user by counting thenumber of keystrokes and the time needed to complete each task.andP;  Accuracy istested by noting the completion or incompletion of a task.andP;  The Judd Testincludes both scores in its final reports.andM;You can choose from three types of reports.andP;  The first, a test summary, canbe presented to the user at the conclusion of the test.andP;  The second, ascreen-only report available from a separate module, lists accuracy andefficiency scores for all test takers.andP;  This report gives you a comparison ofeveryone who has been tested.andP;  The third type is a detailed assessment ofeach test taker, showing the keystroke-by-keystroke response, the time takento complete each task, and the expected versus completed keystrokes and timesfor each task.andM;Because The Judd Test is an external program that operates &quot;on top of &quot;1-2-3, testing occurs within a genuine 1-2-3 environment.andP;  To use thepackage, you need a running copy of 1-2-3.andP;  For $50, Mentrix supplies a&quot;disabled&quot; version of 1-2-3 that lets you run the tests but eliminates1-2-3's printing and filing capabilities.andM;-G.andP;  R.andM;The Judd Test for Lotus 1-2-3.andP;  Mentrix, 103 Providence Mine Rd., Suite 201,Nevada City, CA 95959; 916-265-4000.andP;  Requires 1-2-3 Release 1A, 2, 2.01, or2.2 and DOS 2.0 or higher, First-year license, $495; then, $295 per year.andO;Special pricing available.andO;</TEXT></DOC>